headline: Dover Announces 2025 Scholarship Program Winners
summary: Dover Corporation (NYSE: DOV) today announced the names of 31 recipients of its Dover Foundation Scholars Program. This year's winners represent all five of Dover's operating segments and nearly all of its Operating Companies.
